phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common StateFlow mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Exposing mutable | Use `asStateFlow()` |
| Not using update | Use `update { }` |
| No scope | Use `viewModelScope` |
| Not StateFlow | Use `MutableStateFlow` |
| Not collecting | Use `collectAsState()` |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Use asStateFlow
private val _counter = MutableStateFlow(0)
val counter: StateFlow<Int> = _counter.asStateFlow()

// 2. Use update
fun increment() {
    _counter.update { it + 1 }
}

// 3. Use viewModelScope
fun doWork() {
    viewModelScope.launch {
        delay(1000)
    }
}

// 4. Use StateFlow
private val _data = MutableStateFlow("")

// 5. Collect in Composable
val counter by viewModel.counter.collectAsState()
```

